gnat.server.dictionary
Class Dictionary

java.lang.Object
  gnat.server.dictionary.Dictionary

public class Dictionary
extends java.lang.Object

Dictionaries are used for the recognition of entities.

How to get to a final dictionary?

  • extract names and synonyms from a database: MakeLexiconList or GeneInfo2Dictionary
  • check the lexicon, remove spurious entries: LexiconChecker
  • convert lexicon format: from one gene per line to one ID / name pair per line: ConvertDictionaryToIDNamePairs
  • generate regular expressions for each name: GeneNamesToMWT
  • generate the final automaton: Dictionary
  • run dictionary as server: DictionaryServer
Classes in italics are not contained in this release.

Check dictionaries/readme.dictionaries.txt for additional information.

Author:
Conrad, Joerg
